@startuml 时序图-记录梦境
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE

title 时序图：记录梦境

actor 用户 as User
participant "DreamController" as Controller
participant "DreamService" as Service
participant "TagService" as TagSvc
participant "Dream" as Dream
participant "Tag" as Tag
database "数据库" as DB

User -> Controller: 提交梦境内容（文字/语音/图片、标签、情绪）
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: createDream(dreamData)
activate Service

Service -> TagSvc: getRecommendedTags()
activate TagSvc
TagSvc -> DB: 查询推荐标签
DB --> TagSvc: 返回标签列表
TagSvc --> Service: List<Tag>

Service -> TagSvc: addTagToDream(dreamId, tagIds)
TagSvc -> DB: 保存梦境-标签关联
DB --> TagSvc: 成功

Service -> Dream: create()
activate Dream
Dream -> DB: 插入梦境记录
DB --> Dream: 返回梦境ID
Dream --> Service: Dream

Service --> Controller: Dream
deactivate Service
deactivate TagSvc

Controller --> User: 返回成功，跳转梦境详情
deactivate Controller

@enduml
